This is a preview/Intro/Background to the upcoming movie about Steve Jobs. The life of Apple mastermind Steve Jobs (Michael Fassbender) is revealed in this hard-hitting biopic from director Danny Boyle and scriptwriter Aaron Sorkin (The Social Network). Michael Fassbender delivers a layered, balanced performance as the mercurial Jobs with Kate Winslet similarly impressive as his marketing partner and all-round conscience Joanna Hoffman. Unconventionally based backstage at three different product launches spanning 1984 to 1998 with the iMac, this dramatized profile shows how a successful biopic should be made
